questions.question: A person is behind an object o1 and is also touching another object o2. Later, the person moves to be in front of o2 and is not looking at o2.
questions.dsl: (behind(o0, o1), touching(o0, o2)); object(o0, 'person'); (in_front_of(o0, o2), not_looking_at(o0, o2))

questions.question: Initially, a person is holding an object o1 and is in front of another object o2. Subsequently, this person is holding o2, and finally, the person is behind o1.
questions.dsl: (holding(o0, o1), in_front_of(o0, o2)); (holding(o0, o2), object(o0, 'person')); behind(o0, o1)

questions.question: A person is not looking at an object o1 while simultaneously touching it. Later, the person is on the side of another object o2 while touching it.
questions.dsl: not_looking_at(o0, o1); touching(o0, o1); (object(o0, 'person'), on_the_side_of(o0, o2), touching(o0, o2))

questions.question: A person is in front of an object o1 and not looking at another object o2. Later in the sequence, the person is in o2 and not looking at o1.
questions.dsl: (in_front_of(o0, o1), not_looking_at(o0, o2)); object(o0, 'person'); (in(o0, o2), not_looking_at(o0, o1))

questions.question: A person is holding and touching an object o1, and positioned on the side of another object o2. In a subsequent scene, the person is not looking at o1.
questions.dsl: (holding(o0, o1), on_the_side_of(o0, o2), touching(o0, o1)); object(o0, 'person'); not_looking_at(o0, o1)

questions.question: A person is not looking at object o1 while sitting on another object o2. Following this, the person is leaning on o2 and not looking at o2.
questions.dsl: (not_looking_at(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person'), sitting_on(o0, o2)); (leaning_on(o0, o2), not_looking_at(o0, o2))

questions.question: Initially, a person is holding object o1 while not making contact with another object o2. Subsequently, the person is not looking at either o1 or o2.
questions.dsl: (holding(o0, o1), not_contacting(o0, o2)); (not_looking_at(o0, o1), not_looking_at(o0, o2), object(o0, 'person'))

questions.question: Initially, a person is behind object o1 without contacting it but is touching another object o2. Later, the person is not looking at o1.
questions.dsl: (behind(o0, o1), not_contacting(o0, o1), touching(o0, o2)); (not_looking_at(o0, o1), object(o0, 'person'))

questions.question: A person is leaning on object o1 while not looking at it. Later, the person is not looking at another object o2. Finally, the person is positioned beneath o2.
questions.dsl: (leaning_on(o0, o1), not_looking_at(o0, o1)); not_looking_at(o0, o2); (beneath(o0, o2), object(o0, 'person'))

questions.question: Initially, a person is beneath object o1 and touching another object o2. Subsequently, the person is looking at o1 while not looking at o2.
questions.dsl: beneath(o0, o1); touching(o0, o2); (looking_at(o0, o1), not_looking_at(o0, o2), object(o0, 'person'))
